  <h3>Before this incident:</h3>
  <p>My  child’s teacher or other school staff expressed specific concerns about my child’s  behavior to a special education director or administrator.</p>
</div>  
<h2>Response:</h2>
<p>If misconduct occurs after a, teacher, or other school staff  member expresses specific concerns about a pattern of behavior demonstrated by  the child, the school must follow special education discipline procedures as if  the child were already on an IEP.<sup class="statute">1</sup></p>
